=====
IPIFY
=====

No bullshit express.js app that returns the client ip address.


INSTALL
=======

  git clone http://github.com/chebro/ipify
  npm ci


RUN LOCALLY
===========

  PORT=8080 ADDR=localhost node index.js


BEHIND A REVERSE PROXY
======================

	When behind a reverse proxy, set the `X-Forwarded-For` proxy header to the client IP.

